column3: to enable us to publish your reviews, forum posts, and other content to the TripAdvisor community
column4: to facilitate your booking of travel reservations
column5: to respond to your questions and comments
column6: to measure interest in and improve our products, services, and Website
column7: to notify you about special offers and products or services available from us or our partners that may be of interest to you
column8: to otherwise customize your experience with TripAdvisor, including customizing the ads shown to you
column9: to solicit information from you, including through surveys
column10: to resolve disputes or troubleshoot problems
column11: to prevent potentially prohibited or illegal activities
column12: to enforce our Terms of Use
column13: and as otherwise described to you at the point of collection.",Relevant
